txt.en: 'Well, your search is over - for I am Muirnë!'
'My soft-hearted fool of a sister never understood my desires and has led you on a fool's errand - one that has led you only to your death!'
'You fools! I am Muirnë!  Now die, and fall into darkness!'
'Ah, so you are the ones who have been seeking Muirnë and slaughtering my followers as you go?'
